st.sh

-------------------------------------
onUnderline()
- save line & pos & whether next char is underlined
- clear styling for whole line
- if next char is NOT underlined then underline+bold+navy to next char
- then call refresh() to recalculate

Users can enter "Find & Replace" as-is since we use styling. (But of 
course when passing strings to accelhints lib'y, we must &->&& and 
_->__.)

